    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为：IngressController启动后进入Connecting，同时和LoadBalancer建立关系；连成功后到Connected，再到Idle。那如果连接失败呢？还有请求处理时的状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "Connected",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连接失败走Timeout，超时后需要重新去找LoadBalancer。正常流程是Idle收到请求后进入Sending发送，发完回到Idle。但Sending也可能超时，同样走Timeout。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "[Infra_LoadBalancer]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Sending有两个出口，一个是正常完成回Idle，另一个是超时到Timeout。Timeout统一回LoadBalancer重新调度。还有Closed状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sending",
        "Idle",
        "Timeout",
        "[Infra_LoadBalancer]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Idle可以主动关闭到Closed，Closed之后也回到LoadBalancer，相当于资源释放后重新进入调度池。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Closed",
        "[Infra_LoadBalancer]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：IngressController到Connecting，Connecting分叉到LoadBalancer和Connected，Connected到Idle，然后Idle到Sending和Closed两条线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[Infra_IngressController]",
        "Connecting",
        "[Infra_LoadBalancer]",
        "Connected",
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Closed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
