      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Sending到Idle的箭头别忘了，还有Sending和Idle都要能到Timeout。检查一下Timeout的出边，只能到LoadBalancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sending",
        "Idle",
        "Timeout",
