      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都加上了：Sending返回Idle，Sending和Idle都指向Timeout，Timeout指向LoadBalancer，Closed也指向LoadBalancer。整个状态图应该完整了，您看还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
